<item>
 <title>Audio Saints</title>
 <link>https://nashvillemusicians.org/audio-saints</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-picture field-type-imagefield-crop field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Picture:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://nashvillemusicians.org/sites/default/files/audio_saints.JPG&quot; width=&quot;200&quot; height=&quot;150&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-contact-information field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Contact Information:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;John Donahoe&lt;br /&gt;
Cell: 978-302-1188&lt;br /&gt;
Email: jdonahoe@alumni.berklee.edu&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-personnel-instrumentation field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Personnel/Instrumentation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;John Donahoe: Utility on fiddle, mandolin, guitar and saxophone plus vocals&lt;br /&gt;
Gary Pailer: Lead guitar and lead vocals&lt;br /&gt;
Aeron Long: Cajon and hand percussion&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-describe-what-you-do-in-10 field-type-text-long field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Describe &amp;quot;What You Do&amp;quot; in 100 Words or Less:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;If being a saint means that you please a lot of people …. Well then Audio Saints are aptly named. This Trio of guitar, Cajon/Percussion and Utility (fiddle, mandolin, Saxophone) play a huge variety of music from blues to rock to country and Americana. The group is made up of Gary Pailer on Guitar, harmonica and lead vocals. Gary is a talented singer, songwriter, and instrumentalist that hails originally from St Louis, MO. He lived in Southern California for 14 years till he moved to Nashville in 1994. Earon Long on Cajon/percussion and vocals. Earon is a native of Nashville. As the son of a classic country singer he grew up playing drums to covers by such artists as Ray Price, Merle Haggard  and Johnny Cash. John Donahoe is a Utility Player performing on Fiddle, Mandolin, banjo and Saxophone with Audio Saints. John grew up in Sioux Falls, South Dakota and received his music degree from Boston’s Berklee College of music. John is also a Practicing licensed Architect. He has performed extensively through the years playing blues, bluegrass and country music. In 2014 John moved from Boston to Nashville to play music full time.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-musical-style-s- field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Musical Style(s):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/cover-tunes&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Cover Tunes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/music-listening&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Music for Listening&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/requests&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Requests&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/acoustic&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Acoustic&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/americana&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Americana&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/blues&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Blues&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/bluegrass&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Bluegrass&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/country&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Country&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/musical-styles/rbsoul&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;R&amp;amp;B/Soul&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
